                <h1 class="page-title">核心思想</h1>
                <p class="text-muted">Arrow (1962) 的问题意识、核心机制与理论贡献</p>
            </div>

            <!-- 论文概览 -->
            <section class="page-section mb-5" id="overview">
                <h2 class="page-section-h2 mb-3">📑 论文概览</h2>
                <div class="table-responsive">
                    <table class="table table-bordered table-sm">
                        <tr><td class="table-light text-muted" style="width:120px;">英文标题</td><td><em>The Economic Implications of Learning by Doing</em></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="table-light text-muted">中文参考译</td><td>干中学的经济含义</td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="table-light text-muted">作者</td><td>Kenneth J. Arrow（肯尼斯·阿罗，1972年诺奖得主）</td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="table-light text-muted">发表</td><td><em>The Review of Economic Studies</em>, 29(3), June 1962, pp. 155–173</td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="table-light text-muted">学术位置</td><td>内生增长理论开创性先驱；知识溢出与市场失灵理论的早期奠基</td></tr>
